title: 18 Times the Kardashians Overdid It With Their Spray Tans
text:
18 Times the Kardashians Overdid It With Their Spray Tans Meredith Gordon 
Jackson Lee/Splash News Oh Kim, Kourtney, and Khloe Kardashian. We love their style and ballsy work ethic, but on occasion, these girls take the trend of looking picture-perfect a bit too far. You know what we're talking about, right? Yep. Spray tan abuse. 
A little glow makes every gal look like a million bucks. But too much fake tan looks, well ... fake . The Kardashians love attention, but we're guessing they don't want attention for looking a little on the orange side, right? Here are a few of the times they went a little bit overboard while trying to achieve a bronze hue.
